            "value": "Joue un court avertissement ascendant de trois notes."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "tutorial_voiceover_intro": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ca": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "RetroRapid! és un joc de carreres amb 3 carrils. Mou-te a l'esquerra o a la dreta entre les tres posicions. Et reproduirem sons per indicar quins carrils són segurs, i hauràs de moure't ràpid a un carril segur per avançar cotxes i evitar xocar."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "RetroRapid! is a 3-lane racing game. Move left or right between the three positions. We play sounds to indicate which lanes are safe, and you must quickly move into a safe lane to overtake cars and avoid crashing."
          }
        },
        "en-AU": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "RetroRapid! is a 3-lane racing game. Move left or right between the three positions. We play sounds to indicate which lanes are safe, and you must quickly move into a safe lane to overtake cars and avoid crashing."
          }
        },
        "en-CA": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "RetroRapid! is a 3-lane racing game. Move left or right between the three positions. We play sounds to indicate which lanes are safe, and you must quickly move into a safe lane to overtake cars and avoid crashing."
          }
        },
        "en-GB": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "RetroRapid! is a 3-lane racing game. Move left or right between the three positions. We play sounds to indicate which lanes are safe, and you must quickly move into a safe lane to overtake cars and avoid crashing."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "RetroRapid! es un juego de carreras con 3 carriles. Muévete a la izquierda o a la derecha entre las tres posiciones. Reproduciremos sonidos para indicar qué carriles son seguros, y tendrás que moverte rápido a un carril seguro para adelantar coches y evitar chocar."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "RetroRapid! ist ein 3-Spur-Rennspiel. Bewege dich links oder rechts zwischen den drei Positionen. Wir spielen Töne ab, die sichere Spuren anzeigen, und du musst schnell in eine sichere Spur wechseln, um Autos zu überholen und Crashes zu vermeiden."
          }
        },
        "nl": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "RetroRapid! is een racespel met 3 banen. Beweeg links of rechts tussen de drie posities. We spelen geluiden af die aangeven welke banen veilig zijn, en je moet snel naar een veilige baan om auto's in te halen en botsingen te vermijden."
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "RetroRapid! è un gioco di corse a 3 corsie. Muoviti a sinistra o a destra tra le tre posizioni. Riprodiamo suoni per indicare quali corsie sono sicure, e devi spostarti rapidamente in una corsia sicura per sorpassare le auto ed evitare incidenti."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "RetroRapid! est un jeu de course à 3 voies. Déplace-toi à gauche ou à droite entre les trois positions. Nous jouons des sons pour indiquer quelles voies sont sûres, et tu dois te déplacer rapidement vers une voie sûre pour dépasser les voitures et éviter les crashs."
          }
        }
      }
    },
